Specializing in Oriental weaponry is also a hobby of mine.<br>
I am especially fond of Egg Rolls stuffed with Spam.<br>
I guess it is a &quot;sneaky way of killing someone&quot;... but that's the way guys with funny hats do things.<br><br>
But it is a well known fact that Green Berets were not really self proclaimed fighting men... we served in more of an advisory capacity.  We set up SF camps all over Viet Nam to help lost Marines find their discarded underwear.  We used tracker dogs... until the SPCA protested the abuse of innocent killer dogs.  Sky soldiers wore &quot;Tiger Stripe&quot; underwear... Marines had only one stripe in theirs... I guess that is why they were always getting their asses shot off!  Thank God for Jarheads... and M-60's... Thank God for Sparrow Hawk.  Thank God for Spam?<br><br>
